# Node / JavaScript
# =========================
node_modules/
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
pnpm-debug.log*

# Lockfiles (keep committed by default)
# (Intentionally NOT ignoring package-lock.json / yarn.lock / pnpm-lock.yaml)

